  "source_notes": "B.C. in hand, LMR;  PT notes that most online bios give 1947 but his birth certificate quite clearly says 1948.\\n\\nCraft quotes his autobiography \"Still Foolin' 'Em: Where I've Been, Where I'm Going, and Where the Hell Are My Keys?\" (2014), pg. 15, \"On March 14, 1948, at 7:36 am, I arrived at Doctors Hospital in Manhattan, overlooking Gracie Mansion and the East River\". [http://www.amazon.com/Still-Foolin-Em-Where-Going/dp/1250051843/ref=sr_1_76?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1444523022&sr=1-76&keywords=biography#reader_1250051843].\\n\\nSy Scholfield quotes Crystal on Twitter, 14 March 2021, \"A good omen. I woke up at the exact time I was born 73 years ago! 7:30 a.m. My second Covid birthday.. no more please, everyone stay safe for yourself your family and others -we’re getting closer\" [https://twitter.com/BillyCrystal/status/1371151049898172417].\\n",
